{"tid":162004,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【情報】Switch遊戲更貴的原因：卡帶製造成本高","createTime":"2017-03-19T02:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T07:38:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c37bce13b635d43beaeb49419b019614ce11087f","tid":162004,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T02:57:38.000Z","msg":"2017-03-14 12:49<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-03-10-why-nintendo-switch-games-are-ending-up-more-expensive\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurogamer.net%2Farticles%2F2017-03-10-why-nintendo-switch-games-are-ending-up-more-expensive&d=x%2FNl6Ahg6Nkeqb8F8iTJG10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=56739bb6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-03-10-why-nintendo-switch-games-are-ending-up-more-expensive</a><br />\n在歷經了一波三折的開發之路後，由Tequila Works開發的獨立冒險遊戲《Rime》終於敲定了發售日。這款一開始宣稱PS4獨占的遊戲最終登上了全平台，然而讓人有些意外的是，Switch版的《Rime》售價達到了39.99美元，這要比PS4/Xbox One/PC版貴了整整10美元。<br />\n<br />\nTequila Works給出的官方答覆是：&ldquo;我們是依據各個平台的開發成本和生產成本對產品進行定價的&rdquo;，所以具體的原因到底是什麼呢？<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.crossmap.com/images/2/94/29418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.crossmap.com%2Fimages%2F2%2F94%2F29418.jpg&h=399d177f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSwitch得多花10美元才能玩到《Rime》<br />\n<br />\n外媒Eurogamer就Switch遊戲的定價問題聯繫到了幾家開發商，並得出了結論：正如不少玩家猜測的那樣，這主要是因為Switch卡帶的製造成本要比藍光光碟更高。 並且，Switch的卡帶容量各不相同，有1GB、2GB、4GB、16GB，最大的可達32GB。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/indieobscura-www/assets/editorial/2017/03/Nintendo_Switch-16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.amazonaws.com%2Findieobscura-www%2Fassets%2Feditorial%2F2017%2F03%2FNintendo_Switch-16.jpg&h=9827cd86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當卡帶的容量越大，其製造成本就會越高。同時，卡帶的成本還和生產的數量有關，數量越少，其單價就越高（和印刷的原理一樣）。<br />\n<br />\n那麼為什麼eShop裡的《Rime》也要賣39.99美元呢？Eurogamer在調查中得知，根據任天堂的政策，所有遊戲的數位版售價必須和實體版一樣。這一做法也完全可以理解，否則像Gamestop、GAME這樣的大型零售商可能就不太願意賣Switch遊戲了。<br />\n<br />\n當然，對小型開發商而言這個問題也有解決的辦法，那就是只推出數位版遊戲，這樣就不必考慮卡帶帶來的額外成本了。<br />\n<br />\n《Snake Pass》是一款即將於本月末登陸Switch的遊戲，屆時只有數位版，其開發商Sumo在接受採訪時表示：&ldquo;對我們而言，最重要的是玩家們不應該因為他們選擇了某個平台而受到懲罰。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"6791138430524048d509eab24d82b7677610cd25","tid":162004,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:05:03.000Z","msg":"唔要層chemical coating會唔會平啲"},{"pid":"6c08f7672b49cb1ebb816c9b1e2b456523c69a26","tid":162004,"uid":34551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 謂埋老任收幾錢卡帶專利費先啦"},{"pid":"9e7e3eb43c695e98f2741723ed66ea8f8fd119ed","tid":162004,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:11:14.000Z","msg":"老任真係好撚鍾意出卡帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ba51cdebbc3a17822088b66827489223c33e8d","tid":162004,"uid":34551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老任真係好撚鍾意出卡帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手提機唔用帶可以點sosad"},{"pid":"2f5f71b2da16a0f1c51387c903c3b61d6316c4e0","tid":162004,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老任真係好撚鍾意出卡帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手提機唔用帶可以點sosad</blockquote><br />\ndownload<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d099136e04df8d9b85dda3165911295e1fb85b","tid":162004,"uid":43016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老任真係好撚鍾意出卡帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手提機唔用帶可以點sosad</blockquote><br />\ndownload<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" 